Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:09.74,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}轻舞在 伸出的手掌中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:24.22,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}交错的轻舟溅起水花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:31.83,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}你的笑容 让我无比眷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:37.07,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}多想与你再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:37.07,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:44.11,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}即便相隔着遥远的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:51.15,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}也能感觉到你温暖的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:58.79,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}那就是与你相守的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:02.06,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不管在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:09.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}都与你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
